Temperature limit
Adjust master GPU temperature limit, if it is supported by graphics card.

Hints:
- When GPU synchronization mode is enabled any changes applied to the master GPU are also mirrored to all similar GPUs installed in the system.
- When this slider is focused, you may use cursor keys on your keyboard to finetune the limit.
- You may click the adjacent edit field to directly type in a desired temperature limit.
- You may disable user interface tooltips via <User interface> tab in advanced properties.
